    or number of frames, we need to make the following changes:
    - Live: NOT_USED
            FG_ON
            FG_SPLICE
            RETIRED
            BG_OFF
            BG_SPLICE
            FG_CLEANUP
            FG_ON
    - The live channel will not be deleted, but becomes RETIRED and is
      waiting on its term to become foreground again.


