  - Reliability is about 1 hr.  Had bad pidBuf link while count pic TPs.

  - Support of closed GOP
    - Renamed exitPicFnd to bndryPicFnd so that it can be used for both
      FG and BG channels.
    - For BG channel, when entry pic is found with closed GOP, only bndryPicFnd
      will be set.  Then after the next picture is read, exit time will be
      determined and spliceReady will also be set.

  - closed GOP code seems to work.


